#. type: Plain text
#: ../_posts/2023-07-07-this-week-in-rails.markdown:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Add an option to preprocess Active Storage variants in background job](https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/47473)  \n"
msgstr "[バックグラウンドのジョブでActive Storageの変種を前処理するオプションを追加](https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/47473)  \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../_posts/2023-07-07-this-week-in-rails.markdown:14
msgid ""
"Active Storage variants are processed on the fly when they are needed but "
"sometimes we're sure that they are accessed and want to process them upfront."
msgstr ""
"Active Storageの変種 (variant) は必要なときにその場で処理されます。\n"
"しかしこれらがアクセス済みであれば予め処理しておきたいことがあります。"

#. type: Fenced code block (ruby)
#: ../_posts/2023-07-07-this-week-in-rails.markdown:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"class User < ApplicationRecord\n"
"  has_one_attached :avatar do |attachable|\n"
"    attachable.variant :thumb, resize_to_limit: [100, 100], preprocessed: true\n"
"  end\n"
"end\n"
msgstr ""
"class User < ApplicationRecord\n"
"  has_one_attached :avatar do |attachable|\n"
"    attachable.variant :thumb, resize_to_limit: [100, 100], preprocessed: true\n"
"  end\n"
"end\n"

