msgid "[Improve performance of ActiveSupport::JSON.encode](https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/48614)  \n"
msgstr "[ActiveSupport::JSON.encodeの効率を向上](https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/48614)  \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../_posts/2023-07-07-this-week-in-rails.markdown:28
