"This about doubles the performance of `.to_json`/`ActiveSupport::JSON."
"encode`. The benchmarks are included in the pull request."
msgstr ""
"`.to_json`/`ActiveSupport::JSON.encode`の性能が約2倍になります。\n"
"プルリクエストにベンチマークが含まれています。"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../_posts/2023-07-07-this-week-in-rails.markdown:29
